{"tid":868253,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(ps4 / switch / xbox) Starlink: Battle for Atlas 有冇爸打一起討論","createTime":"2018-10-19T10:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T15:04:41.000Z","uid":82515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f09040917976fd9351812540d0c03689a2e348","tid":868253,"uid":82515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rm0QWwK6ZLk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRm0QWwK6ZLk&d=JNKOYaxhaqxPleht%2BagRYywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e5fc1da7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rm0QWwK6ZLk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RCza4n4h4yU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRCza4n4h4yU&d=JNKOYaxhaqxPleht%2BagRYywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=baa93f31\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RCza4n4h4yU</a><br />\n<br />\n《銀河聯軍：阿特拉斯之戰》也帶來了橫跨整個星系的 開放遊戲 世界，讓玩家全然自由地盡情探索。採用 Snowdrop 引擎全新打造的這款遊戲，營造了遼闊的阿特拉斯星系外星世界，並提供七顆充滿各式生命和獨特挑戰的星球，任玩家無接縫地穿梭其中。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Nintendo Switch 版本的專屬追加內容，可讓《銀河聯軍》裡的眾多角色與頂尖飛行員暨星際火狐戰隊領袖火狐．麥克勞德並肩作戰及駕駛他著名的艾英星艦。玩家可以使用火狐．麥克勞德遊玩整個戰役，並在阿特拉斯星系中執行擊敗星際火狐戰隊的死對頭沃爾夫．歐唐納的獨特任務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.n3rdabl3.com/wp-content/images/uploads/2017/06/DCJi5BcW0AA27VA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.n3rdabl3.com%2Fwp-content%2Fimages%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FDCJi5BcW0AA27VA.jpg&h=c67aca00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/jollykill.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/starlink-is-the-family-friendly-no-mans-sky-i-didnt-know-i-wanted.jpg?w=650&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fjollykill.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fstarlink-is-the-family-friendly-no-mans-sky-i-didnt-know-i-wanted.jpg%3Fw%3D650%26ssl%3D1&h=58bc0d64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左 Starfox starter set <br />\n隻機插起手制後面會有藍燈著, 其實幾靚..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDigital +加DLC set 聽講有晒全武器 加隊員 (好似最抵, 但睇完TRAILER 見佢可以實物咁逐隻機體MIX &amp; MATCH 機翼 同武器 好似好正, 我認有D幼稚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n原來按住ZOOM IN , 可以用體感瞄準<br />\n<br />\n有冇爸打玩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fcec5bff60bc035865e232ed157976dc767cf4","tid":868253,"uid":11082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"睇下gameplay先"},{"pid":"ce13520cae4c5e7c5b20ae7818a2938fb60401a6","tid":868253,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"反而想知邊度有飛機同武器賣？ 唔想上Amazon訂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cd1df5f38cf6847e8b1a01babf900b363a6f35","tid":868253,"uid":64058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce13520cae4c5e7c5b20ae7818a2938fb60401a6","tid":868253,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"反而想知邊度有飛機同武器賣？ 唔想上Amazon訂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"信和有, 間間都有放係玻璃櫃, 見到ps4 starter set $480"},{"pid":"ec21e0c6616ac16514530f8645f34105930ffc19","tid":868253,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72cd1df5f38cf6847e8b1a01babf900b363a6f35","tid":868253,"uid":64058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce13520cae4c5e7c5b20ae7818a2938fb60401a6","tid":868253,"uid":89056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"反而想知邊度有飛機同武器賣？ 唔想上Amazon訂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <